# Black Gold Connect

Official Black Gold Connect website, digital business cards, and team directory.

## Brand Colours
- Black Gold Gold: RGB 198, 150, 83 / HEX #C69653
- Response Green: RGB 110, 190, 68 / HEX #6EBE44

## Updating Employee Information
Employee pages are located in `/employees/`. Update phone numbers, titles, emails, and vCards as required.

## NFC Card Use
Write the employee profile URL to the NFC card using NFC Tools > Write > Add a record > URL / URI.
